channel.title: Plz help im almost done with my server :D
channel.description:
hey guys so I followed this tut on how to add castlewars: http://www.google.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/tutorials/220638-castle-wars-delta.html (replace "Google" with "rune-server") everything works really good until I go into the waiting room I wait until it finishes counting and then nothing happens :( it just starts counting down again.
I think its because the code that makes it teleport me to castlewars when it finishes counting down isn't even written but I'm not sure and i do not have the code and do not know how to make one so please help me out I would be so thankful
